timeline.bodyText:
Hm... seems we lost the feature to skip the BOM...
The simplest way would be probably:
StringBuilder buffer = sourceCode.getCodeBuffer();
Reader reader;

if (buffer.charAt(0) == '\uFEFF') {
    // skip BOM if present
    reader = new CharSequenceReader(buffer.substring(1));
} else {
    reader = new CharSequenceReader(buffer);
}
return new JspTokenManager(reader);

